  <brief_title>Extension Study to Assess the Safety and Efficacy of Pasireotide in Patients With Cushing's Disease</brief_title>
  <official_title>Extension Study to Assess the Safety and Efficacy of Pasireotide in Patients With Cushing's Disease</official_title>
